        <arrangement id="ref37">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>The photographs in the Fred McDarrah Collection are arranged chronologically. Three oversize prints are housed in a map case separate from the rest of the items. Work titles and dates are derived from McDarrah's own annotations on each print.</p>
        </arrangement>
        <custodhist id="ref51">
            <head>Provenance</head>
            <p>The Fred W. McDarrah Gay Pride Photographs Collection was donated to the Fales Library by Fred McDarrah in 2006.</p>
        </custodhist>
